This paper deals with reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). It also involves optimization and decision-making, which are common topics in machine learning (cs.LG) and robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses the formulation of the problem as a traveling salesman problem, which is a classic problem in computer science and optimization (cs.DS). Finally, the paper deals with policies and their performance, which is a topic in control systems (cs.SY).
